member.name: M:ArcGIS.Desktop.Internal.GeoProcessing.na_QueryCredits.SolveCreditsEstimator.EstimateCredits(System.String,ArcGIS.Desktop.Internal.GeoProcessing.Controls.IValueControl[])
member.summary:
returns (double credits_estimate, double credits_available, bool canShow_credits_available) tuple
credits_estimate < 0 => show credits unavailable warning
credits_available is double.NegativeInfinity => ignore available credits
canShow_credits_available is false => do not show available credits value but still use in compariosn with estimate if estimate is non-negative and available is finite
canShow_credits_available is true => show available credits value to user if finite (and has non-negative estimate)
if an exception is thrown the banner will show error status message with exception string.
